<div class="mt-16 md:mt-0">
  <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight text-center">
    Everything you need to start IP subnetting for your work.
  </h2>
  <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600">
    This subnet calculator tool empowers you to easily obtain subnet addresses and the number of available hosts within a given network. Created by a network engineer, this tool simplifies the subnetting process, making it more accessible for network engineers, students, and anyone who needs to
    perform subnetting calculations. </br> </br>
    Subnetting is the crucial process of dividing a network into smaller subnetworks, or subnets, to enhance network performance, improve security, and efficiently manage network resources. This tool provides a valuable resource for anyone learning or working with networks.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 mt-16 gap-16">
  {
